snippet.title: Best VGM 1844 - Arcana - Shrine for the Worship of Chaos
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 654 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kk0QDbYvtAQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Arcana (1992)
Shrine for the Worship of Chaos
Jun Ishikawa
